</p>
<div id='interlinear'><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:Πᾶσα' title='Pasa: Every'><font color='#000000'>Πᾶσα</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:Πᾶσα' title='1) Every'><font color='#000000'> Every</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ἀλγηδὼν' title='algedon: pain'><font color='#000000'>ἀλγηδὼν</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ἀλγηδὼν' title='2) pain'><font color='#000000'> pain</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:εὐκαταφρόνητος' title='eukataphronetos: easy to disregard'><font color='#000000'>εὐκαταφρόνητος&#903;</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:εὐκαταφρόνητος' title='3) easy to disregard'><font color='#000000'>(is) easy to disregard</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ἡ' title='he: the'><font color='#000000'>ἡ</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:ἡ' title='4) the'><font color='#000000'>→</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:γὰρ' title='gar:for'><font color='#000000'>γὰρ</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:γὰρ' title='5) for; because'><font color='#000000'>because</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></span><span><p class='script150'><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php?title=Template:GED:σύντονον' title='syntonon: intense'><font color='#000000'>σύντονον</font></a>&nbsp;</p><br><p><a href='http://wiki.epicurism.info/iurl/index.php